lines.text:
[as he is hanging DiAngelo with his own tie]
Know what I'm gonna do, huh?... Figure it out, DiAngelo, figure it out... I'm gonna send you to wap heaven... I'm gonna make you famous, DiAngelo... YOU'RE GONNA BE THE FIRST WHITEY EVER HUNG BY A NIGGER!

[to Zach]
You need a whooping, Boy!
Boy?... Where you see a boy?
And I'm gonna do it with these own two hands!
Old man gonna whoop my ass?
[Papa and Zach have it out with each other]
